Qatar Warns Against ‘Unjustified’ Price Rises, Al Raya Says

-- B y   R o b e r t   T u t t l e
-- 
2011-09-08T07:06:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/qatar-warns-against-unjustified-price-rises-al-raya-says.html
Qatari Business and Trade Minister
Jassim bin Abdul Aziz bin Jassim bin Hamad Al Thani said his
ministry will intensify efforts to crack down on “unjustified”
price increases after the government raised public sector
salaries earlier this month,  Al Raya newspaper  said, citing an
interview with the minister.  The government yesterday announced that public sector
civilian and military salaries would be raised by as much as 120
percent starting this month, Qatar News Agency reported
yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Robert Tuttle in Doha at 
 rtuttle@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
